Tyrael came out of the lab and looked around. It seemed that Kaiser,
Darkangel, Blackheart or anyone else had gone in another room. He
opened his communicator.

Tyrael: General Blackheart, I am currently working on a very
precarious project and I request the authorization to lock Lab 48-A. I
would also need some assistance to move a stasis pod to that lab.
